#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arcade"
msgstr "Arkadna"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of possible players:"
msgstr "Število možnih igralcev:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>One</para>"
msgstr "<para>En</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&bomber; is a single player arcade game. The player is invading various "
"cities in a plane that is decreasing in height."
msgstr ""
"&bomber; je arkadna igra za enega igralca. Igralec napada različna mesta v "
"ravnini, ki se zmanjšuje v višino."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The goal of the game is to destroy all the buildings and advance to the next "
"level. Each level gets a harder by increasing the speed of the plane and the "
"height of the buildings."
msgstr ""
"Cilj igre je uničiti vse zgradbe in napredovati na naslednjo stopnjo. Vsaka "
"raven postane težja s povečanjem hitrosti letala in višine zgradb."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "How To Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "&bomber; main screen"
msgstr "&bomber; glavni zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player is flying a plane in a city. The plane flies from left to right. "
"Every time it disappears off the side of the play area, it reappears on the "
"left side again, but lower than it was before."
msgstr ""
"Igralec vozi letalo v mestu. Letalo leti od leve proti desni. Vsakič, ko "
"izgine ob strani igrišča, se ponovno pojavi na levi strani, vendar nižje, "
"kot je bil prej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player has to destroy all the buildings to clear the level. If the plane "
"crashes into a building, then the player loses a life and the plane is moved "
"to the top left of the play area again."
msgstr ""
"Igralec mora uničiti vse zgradbe, da počisti raven. Če letalo strmoglavi v "
"zgradbo, potem igralec izgubi življenje in letalo se ponovno premakne v "
"zgornji levi del igralne površine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Buildings are destroyed by dropping bombs on them. This can be done by "
"clicking the &LMB; or pressing the &Space; key. The bomb will fall from the "
"plane and hit anything directly below it."
msgstr ""
"Zgradbe so uničene tako, da nanje odvržejo bombe. To lahko storite tako, da "
"kliknete &LMB; ali pritiskom tipke &Space;. Bomba bo padla z letala in "
"zadela karkoli neposredno pod njim."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After clearing a level, the player advances to the next level. Each level "
"gets slightly harder than the previous level as the buildings get taller and "
"the plane gets faster."
msgstr ""
"Po čiščenju ravni igralec napreduje na naslednjo stopnjo. Vsaka stopnja "
"postane nekoliko težja od prejšnje stopnje, saj so stavbe višje in letalo "
"hitrejše."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &bomber; configuration dialog allows you to select visual themes for "
"&bomber;."
msgstr ""
"&bomber; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno vam omogoča izbiro vizualnih tem za "
"&bomber;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a new theme simply choose the theme from the selection list. Each "
"item in the list shows a small preview left to the theme name. A selection "
"is immediately applied."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati novo temo, preprosto izberite temo na izbirnem seznamu. "
"Vsak element na seznamu prikazuje majhen predogled levo od imena teme. Izbor "
"se takoj uporabi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are satisfied with the theme you have selected you can click the "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton> button, located at the bottom part of this "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste zadovoljni z izbrano temo, lahko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Zapri</"
"guibutton>, ki se nahaja na dnu tega pogovornega okna."

